{
  "id": "63c1913e76288b001df0a30e",
  "title": "音律の比較",
  "created": 1673630015,
  "updated": 1673807089,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c1913e76288b001df0a30e",
      "text": "音律の比較",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630015,
      "updated": 1673630015
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1913eaff09e00006ed362",
      "text": "音律の比較",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630015,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6de8",
      "text": "\t[*** [ピタゴラス音律]] 1, 9/8, 81/64, 4/3, 3/2, 27/16, 243/128, 2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806919
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6de9",
      "text": "\t\t> 音階の全ての音と音程を周波数比3:2の純正な[完全五度]に基づいて導出する音律 [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ピタゴラス音律 ピタゴラス音律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dea",
      "text": "\t\t1:2は「オクターブ違い、同じ音名」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6deb",
      "text": "\t\tある適当な音Dから上下に3:2を3回やることで7音からなる音階ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dec",
      "text": "\t\t　これは現代の平均律の白鍵から半音の6%程度のズレに収まっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6ded",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/e77e2c0792fae93b1231feae47372f95]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dee",
      "text": "　　これをもっと繰り返していくと、全音階よりも「少し高い音」「少し低い音」ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6def",
      "text": "　　　それがシャープとフラットになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df0",
      "text": "　　　この時点ではドのシャープとレのフラットは違う音だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df1",
      "text": "　　　[https://gyazo.com/7d0f483d34c2d19a09201958c90205fa]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df2",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ピタゴラスコンマ ピタゴラスコンマ - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tG# - Ab = `log(3, 2) * 12 % 1` = 0.01955000865387646",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673807089
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t　これが0になるならオクターブ違いの同じ音とみなせるのたが、実際にはズレがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t`_ * 12` = 0.23460010384651753",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t　このズレは1/4半音程度だとわかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df7",
      "text": "\t[*** [純正律]] 1, 9/8, 5/4, 4/3, 3/2, 5/3, 15/8, 2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806913
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df8",
      "text": "　　>Cを基準とした場合、Cの3度上がE、5度上がG、次にGの3度上がB、5度上がD、さらにCの5度下がF、Fの3度上がAとなり、これらを1 オクターヴ内に配列することでハ長調の全音階が得られる。 [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/純正律 純正律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6df9",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/5820277b801d1dfd83bf42fbbc5d72c9]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dfa",
      "text": "\t　幹音から5/4倍することでシャープの半音が、4/5倍することでフラットの半音が得られる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dfb",
      "text": "\t　　[https://gyazo.com/b0c842b797808a84e4b078de35495d13]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dfc",
      "text": "　　　ラのシャープとソのフラットは存在しないって理解でいいのかな？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dfd",
      "text": "　　　　今でもそういう書き方はあまりしないのは、これが理由なのかな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806989
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4448eaff09e0000ba6e19",
      "text": "　　　　\tA#ではなくBb, GbではなくF#って書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806990,
      "updated": 1673807027
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dfe",
      "text": "　　  ドのシャープとレのフラットはもちろん違う音",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6dff",
      "text": "\t[*** [平均律]] [$ (\\sqrt[12]{2})^n ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806907
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e00",
      "text": "\t\t>十二平均律とは、1オクターヴを12等分した音律である。隣り合う音（半音）の周波数比は等しく[$ (\\sqrt[12]{2})^n : 1 ] となる。[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/平均律 平均律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e01",
      "text": "\t　「1オクターブは12半音である」と考えて、半音の周波数比率を平均化して同じ比率にした",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e02",
      "text": "\t\tドのシャープとレのフラットが同じ音になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e03",
      "text": "\t\t\t「Q: なんで同じ音に2通りの表記があるの？ A:昔は違ったんだよ」 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806884
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e04",
      "text": "\t\t>[フレット式楽器]やモノコードなどでは、幾何的に弦の分割点を設定することで平均律を実現できる。また、フレット式楽器では、平均律以外の半音の音程が一定でない音律では、各弦に対するフレット間隔が揃わず、直線のフレットを用いるには不都合である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806881
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e08",
      "text": "\t\t\tなるほど[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0a",
      "text": "\ttable::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0b",
      "text": "\t \t平均律\t純正律\t\tピタ\t",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0c",
      "text": "\t D\t0\t0\t1/1\t0\t1/1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0d",
      "text": "\t Eb\t100\t\t\t90\t256/243",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0e",
      "text": "\t E\t200\t204\t9/8\t204\t9/8",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e0f",
      "text": "\t  F\t300\t\t\t294\t32/27",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e10",
      "text": "\t F#\t400\t386\t5/4\t408\t81/64",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e11",
      "text": "\t G\t500\t498\t4/3\t498\t4/3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e12",
      "text": "\t G#\t600\t\t\t612\t729/512",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e13",
      "text": "\t A\t700\t702\t3/2\t702\t3/2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e14",
      "text": "\t Bb\t800\t\t\t792\t128/81",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e15",
      "text": "\t B\t900\t884\t5/3\t906\t27/16",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e16",
      "text": "\t C\t1000\t\t\t996\t16/9",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e17",
      "text": "\t C#\t1100\t1088\t15/8\t1110\t243/128",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673806875,
      "updated": 1673806875
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4441aaff09e0000ba6e18",
